quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  52,1,"Mi woo…óndirii [Fello] Tuuri ngo!"
  52,2,"E deftere winndaande nde,"
  52,3,"e …óeer portaa…ói!"
  52,4,"E Suudu wuurnraandu ndu!"
  52,5,"E Kippoodi (mboodi)toowundi ndi"
  52,6,"E maayo heewno ngo!"
  52,7,"Pellet, lepte Jooma …óe ko janooje."
  52,8,"Ala du√Īoowo …óe."
  52,9,"√Ďande kammu ngu dillirta dillere,"
  52,10,"pelle …óeen njaha e jahgol,"
  52,11,"haray nden √Īande, bone woodanii yeddu…ďe …ďe."
  52,12,"…ďeen won…ďe e jumpugol, he…ďe pija."
  52,13,"√Ďande …ďe du√Īiroytee doole e Yiite Jahannama du√Īannde,"
  52,14,"[∆Āe mbi'anee] : ""Ko ngee Yiite woni ko njeddtno…óon."
  52,15,"E ko mbilewu nii? Kaa hara on ngla yi'ide?"
  52,16,"Cumee e magge! Mu√Ī√Īi…óon ma on mu√Ī√Īaaki, fof no fota e mon. Nganndee ko njo…ďete…óon, ko ko ngollayno…óon""."
  52,17,"Pellet, gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen hino e Aljannaaji e neemaaji,"
  52,18,"ko …ďe dakimitotoo…ďe ko Joomi ma…ď…ďe okki …ďe, Joomi ma…ď…ďe da…óndi …ďe lepte Jahiimi …óeen."
  52,19,"[∆Āe mbi'anee] : ""√Ďaamee njaron, ko newi mo…ódeum, sabu koko ngollayno…óon."
  52,20,"hara ko on so…ď…ďindii…ďe e hoore dan…óe weertindiraa…óe"", Min ndesina …ďe kadi yoo…óa e yaaJa gite en"
  52,21,"∆Āeen gooŇč…óin…ďe, ge√Īngol ma…ď…ďe ngol kadi jokki …ďe e gooŇč…óinal, Min tawtindinay …ďe e ge√Īngol ma…ď…ďe ngol. Min istantaa …ďe hu'unde e golle ma…ď…ďe …óeen; ne…ó…óo kala ko faggitii kon no tiginaa."
  52,22,"Min …ďeydani …ďe muuyantee…ói e tebbeeli kala ko …ďe tuuyetee."
  52,23,"He…ďe nja…ďondira toon, √Īeddu…óe …óe jillaa mehre wonaa ko bakkondinta."
  52,24,"Sukaa…ďe no eeltanaa…ďe hino wanngoo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, wa'a…ďe wa kaŇčŇče maraa…óe."
  52,25,"Yoga ma…ď…ďe feewtita yoga, …ďe la…ďndondira;"
  52,26,"…ďe mbi'a: ""Pellet, min laatino ado [hannde], hulnoo…ďe [lepte …óeen] hakkunde yim…ďe amen"";"
  52,27,"Allah mo∆ī∆īii e amen, O da…óni meon lepte Norngal."
  52,28,"Min laatino ado [hannde], torotonoo…ďe Mo. Pellet, ko KaŇčko woni mo∆ī∆īo, jurmotoo…óo too…óo on""."
  52,29,"Anndintin tan, sabu neema Joomi maa oon, a wonaa ndureejo wonaa a kaangaa…óo."
  52,30,"Kaa …ďe mb'ay won'de : ""Ko jimoowo ! Min habbitani mo tan jikke maayde""."
  52,31,"Maaku : ""kabbitee ! Miin kadi mi…óo habbitodi e mon""."
  52,32,"Kaa ko haqqille ma…ď…ďe …óeen yamir…ďe …óuum? Kaa hara ko …ďe yim…ďe bew…ďe tan?"
  52,33,"Kaa …ďe mbi'ay won'de : ""O sincu nde?"" Si ko woni, wonaa …ďe gooŇč…óinoo…ďe."
  52,34,"Yoo …ďe ngaddu yeewtere sugu mayre, si wonii ko …ďe gooŇč…óu…ďe."
  52,35,"Kaa …ďe tagira …ďaawo tak…óo? Kaa ko kam…ďe ngoni tagoo…ďe …ďen?"
  52,36,"Kaa (ko) kam…ďe tagi kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin? Ko woni kon, …ďe njananaaka."
  52,37,"Kaa …ďe njogiti ngaluuji Joomi maa …óiin? Kaa ko kam…ďe ngoni hu…ďindii…ďe …ďeen?"
  52,38,"Kaa …ďe njogiti …ďargal ngal …ďe njentorta? yoo ke…óitii…óo e ma…ď…ďe oon addu hujja …ďanngu…óo !"
  52,39,"Maa ko …ďi…ó…ďe rew…ďe ngoodanta mo, onon kam wor…ďe …ďeen?"
  52,40,"Kaa a la…ďndi …ďe njo…ďdi, hara jo…ďugol ndi no teddani …ďe?"
  52,41,"Kaa …ďe nganndu fii wirnii…ói …óiin, hara he…ďe mbinnda?"
  52,42,"Maa …ďe paala fewjoore? ko yeddu…ďe …ďeen, woni fooletee…ďe pewje …ďen."
  52,43,"Kaa he…ďe mari dewetee…óo ko woori Allah? Senaare woodanii Allah, e kon ko …ďe cirkata !"
  52,44,"Si …ďe nji'ii ta∆īatine immornde ka kammu no yani, …ďe mbi'a: ""Ko duule pawondir…óe""."
  52,45,"Terto …ďe, haa …ďe kawroya e √Īalaande ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe leptoytee e mum;"
  52,46,"√Ďande nde pewje ma…ď…ďe duncanoytaa …ďe hay hu'unde, …ďe ngonaa kadi walloytee…ďe."
  52,47,"Ko pellet, hino woodani too√Ī…ďe …ďeen, lepte goo ko wonaa …óen …óon. Ko ko …ďuri …óuu…óude kon e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe nganndaa."
  52,48,"Mu√Ī√Īo √Īaawoore Joomi maa ndeen. Tawde pellet, ha…óa e ndenka amen. Seniniraa yettugol Joomi maa, tuma …ďaŇčoto…óaa."
  52,49,"Jehma on kadi, subbunhinano…óaa mo e ka mutugol koode."
